{"tid":2109548,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警偷看供詞 控方︰冇匿埋唔算偷睇","createTime":"2020-07-15T09:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T10:28:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"501d3afad8e3c7f0abb0f12c886afde16c64bf36","tid":2109548,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200715/DF66JEHZUN4WSZLSHSSZHGS45M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2FDF66JEHZUN4WSZLSHSSZHGS45M%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=e617b037\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2FDF66JEHZUN4WSZLSHSSZHGS45M%2F&h=ce923d6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200715/DF66JEHZUN4WSZLSHSSZHGS45M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警偷看供詞 控方︰冇匿埋唔算偷睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uPVWaLVeR0QEpslVpClO_XVIv_8=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HXFIWO7XE53KEPRYLG5A7AGJGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuPVWaLVeR0QEpslVpClO_XVIv_8%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHXFIWO7XE53KEPRYLG5A7AGJGY.jpg&h=6451607c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女警盧卓凝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年7月28日「光復元朗」示威活動中，警員拘捕一名攜有波子及自製發射器的女子，及後控以一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，案件昨續審。辯方大律師郭憬憲直指前日「偷睇」文件的作供女警「誠信跌破零」，事後「以大話冚大話」解釋，影響證供可信性。控方反指在公眾地方看文件不算「偷睇」，<span class=\"orange\">裁判官葉壠亮聞言說：「都有人會明目張膽下犯案嘅」</span>，惹來庭上一片笑聲。<br />\n<br />\n當日負責拘捕被告的衝鋒女警盧卓凝前日出庭作供，惟休庭期間，被辯方法律團隊發現她偷看被列為呈堂文件的警員記事冊影印本。案件主管其後於女警身上撿獲有關文件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告稱發射器為劍術會道具<br />\n<br />\n郭大狀昨指，學堂曾教授警員作供技巧，盧自稱「緊張」云云旨在掩飾犯例，指「偷睇」等於考試「出貓」。曾任職警務人員的案件主控大律師葉劍明反駁指，「我當差都冇學過」，揚言「緊張唔出奇，緊張唔使一定要面抽筋」。裁判官最終裁定被告的招認口供可呈堂。<br />\n<br />\n被告。。。。。。。。。故一同攜帶外出。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC1653/19"},{"pid":"a0a25d92f43f25b36a3ba6ab08720475ecdbe8d9","tid":2109548,"uid":83910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"明搶就唔算偷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e69dd423f3f105d8a0ae43b70875670bc2271b","tid":2109548,"uid":343268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:08:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"818f613d8b40e35393daf7e1cf10f5f8a91ec59a","tid":2109548,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:28:42.000Z","msg":"惹來庭上一片笑聲<br />\n<br />\n孔乙己2020"}]}